0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T18:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900508ffd4d3f73c40be1a2d4ffbee6e4e3157d8","tid":856624,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T19:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2819c24702da28c6a999362cdabf8264c7adb61","tid":856624,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T19:17:27.000Z","msg":"唔係撥冷水 不過你都講學生既力量係好大<br />\n一嚟多少少時間同自由 二嚟熱血啲<br />\n以前都係靠班學生唔怕事咁衝 班大人都拉唔撚住喇<br />\n其實咁倉促遊行我諗唔會有超級多人出現到 唔夠部署<br />\n無左學聯同依家政黨分裂得咁犀利咁細又係麻煩<br />\n最好間間大學佟仆街啲唔好比學生發聲<br />\n等大家條氣唔順反叛番少少<br />\n仲有整番個學聯出嚟 唔好再散沙咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4bdaebbddc107d9f57ae5e0908883a82c913c7","tid":856624,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T19:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a095e498bb6bc755aad8b12fda99a9b7e320903","tid":856624,"uid":191366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T22:04:45.000Z","msg":"團結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  星期日見"},{"pid":"0c58fa67b47dc6e390f2fa8ca9be0ca278395575","tid":856624,"uid":145530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"星期日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}